SARAH BROWN Behind the scenes at Number Ten Downing Street. Former Prime Minister Gordon Brown's wife Sarah gives us the inside story of life in the British PM's official residence. She talks about the pressures of bringing up a young family whilst supporting her husband in running the country. BOOK DETAILS Behind the Black Door - Sarah Brown Publisher: Random House Show less